        <mxCell id="foot" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontColor=#666666;" value="Solid = live in code; dashed / grey = designed, built-but-off, or partial (marker in label: (planned)=spec/design only, (built, off)/(gated)=code-complete but disabled, (partial)=partly shipped). PRAMANA is SOX single-tenant v1 - much of Certification, bulk assign, SAML, GDPR erasure and 5-of-6 frameworks are spec, not runtime. All three apps share the wegofwd-llm seam; PRAMANA + kathai-chithiram also share wegofwd-video (ADR-026); Mentible adds shared wegofwd-secure / wegofwd-help - see shared_library.drawio. Verified against each repo README/docs/ADRs/source, 2026-07-07." vertex="1">
